latestIgtvVideos.title: 𝘼𝙣 𝙚𝙫𝙚𝙣𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙖𝙩 @the_crepe_cafe_ranchi
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Recently I visited a new spot at Ranchi - @the_crepe_cafe_ranchi located at very popular area of the city -Lalpur chowk 📍
God...when you step in... you'll smell coffee & nutella - How mouth watering it is ??
𝗕𝗲𝗳𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝘀𝘁𝗮𝗿𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗼𝗳𝗳 - 𝗜 𝘄𝗼𝘂𝗹𝗱 𝘀𝗮𝘆 𝘁𝗵𝗲𝘆 𝗺𝗮𝗶𝗻𝘁𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗵𝗶𝗴𝗵 𝘀𝗮𝗳𝗲𝘁𝘆 & 𝗵𝘆𝗴𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗲 𝘀𝗼 𝗱𝗼𝗻'𝘁 𝘄𝗼𝗿𝗿𝘆 𝗺𝘂𝗰𝗵!!

I love that this whole café focused their menu on one range that is - 𝙘𝙧ê𝙥𝙚 dishes and coffee... we do have many café here but they sum up all of the dishes leaving the wide range of coffee and 𝙘𝙧ê𝙥𝙚... Also this is a chain of crêpes restaurant... if you are a nutella and coffee lover 😀... then this is your place 🙆
They have a focused menu on wide variety of crêpes..for siders and beverages they have frappè, mocha, cuppacino, and coffees ☕...
Besides that it creates a cozy place with aesthetic playlist of songs that drive your mood... 
well you can visit here anytime but I would prefer to go for breakfast and evening bites (bcoz if these two timings are well spent... then you are heading a good vibe 😊)

throw a visit to - @the_crepe_cafe_ranchi 😊

Videography 📷 - no one but we sister's - @shahastra_singh & me 
editing - @iamscani
Shot on - oppo f9 pro

latestIgtvVideos.title: Cloud makeup with concealer || ft. @arianagrande (Put your 🎧 for 3D sound)
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
hella everyone💕💕💕.... this #quarantine is getting more difficult for us with huge loss in recent... in the time of pandemic your mind is the thing you need to take care of... thus instead of getting sad.. let's just put on earplugs 🎧 & enjoy this video with 3D sound effect.... I attempted this look for the 1st time & yeah I used concealer @nyxcosmetics_in instead of a paint coz I really didn't want to harm my skin ☺😅.... & I didn't even had a typical pink pigmented shadow so I just dabbed few from my lip color 💄 @facescanada ... & made the clouds ☁... .  Seriously it didn't took alot of time as I was expecting.... it simple pretty thing u can try ....

latestIgtvVideos.title: Star #freckles Makeup 💫 Tutorial
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
never thought it's that simple & easy.... this is a wonderful attempt you can try in #quarantine ... though I couldn't update my makeup due to this Lockdown but the products I used is easily available & simple. You can find alternative to this so chill 😀. the basic I used here is @wetnwildindia liquid glitter eyeshadow to make it shine... & simple stationery stars. I did washed it in hot water with a cleanser to avoid dirt... & lastly used @vaselineindia petroleum jelly to stick on my cheeks 💕
